Losing a parent comes with so much grief and pain, no matter how old they are. Sadly, the reality is that they will not be here on earth forever. Nigerian actor and stand-up comedian Stanley Chibuna popularly known as FunnyBone is grieving after his mother kicked the bucket.The heartbroken businessman took to his social media page to share the sad news. Mourning the loss of his mother, FunnyBone shared a blank photo on his Instagram page to show his grief.Â In another post, the actor shared a beautiful photo of his mother, stating that he is pained by his loss, but however, leaves it all to God.Describing his mother as his world, FunnyBone noted that he would miss her forever. Source